extendedInfo.description: The best application of United States for the Play Store for all Americans.In this application you will find the following:- News: From the best Newspaper, all the latest news and press in United States on politics, economy, sports, culture, society and everything about Americans. You have the option to read the newspaper news within our app or in the browser.- Weather: Climate and Weather of United States and all cities in an accessible and quick.- Maps: Complete maps with routes and roads around the country of United States. We use Google Maps, the best mapping system.- Jobs: If you are looking for a job this is your place, using the most important job website for Americans in the Internet.- Videos: The most popular videos in United States this week, for all Americans.At the moment we only have news, weather, maps, jobs and videos, all sections are updated frequently.If you want new sections you just let us know. As well as adding new Newsspaper, Maps, Weather, Jobs or Videos Source.Country Description: The United States of America (commonly called the United States, the U.S., the USA, America, and the States) is a federal constitutional republic consisting of fifty states and a federal district. The country is situated mostly in central North America, where its forty-eight contiguous states and Washington, D.C., the capital district, lie between the Pacific and Atlantic Oceans, bordered by Canada to the north and Mexico to the south. The state of Alaska is in the northwest of the continent, with Canada to the east and Russia to the west across the Bering Strait. The state of Hawaii is an archipelago in the mid-Pacific. The country also possesses several territories in the Pacific and Caribbean. At 3.79 million square miles (9.83 million km2) and with over 314 million people, the United States is the third- or fourth-largest country by total area, and the third-largest by both land area and population. It is one of the world's most ethnically diverse and multicultural nations, the product of large-scale immigration from many countries.
